defaultIn August we published two Status Reports, one on the new Rural Development Programme in England
default and one on Direct Payments
default. The former presented an update on developments with some factual background on Rural Development Programme (RDP), whilst the latter we provided a summary of what has been agreed about the new direct payments system and set out our approach to implementation in England. 
