default              
defaultThe
default Status Report on Direct Payments
default, referred to above,
default describes in detail what has been agreed in the EU, although we still await the final text of the European Direct Payments regulation which is likely to be agreed only in November.
default 
defaultMany of the main parameters of the scheme will be defined in that regulation and in the 
defaultCommission
default implementing regulations which will be agreed in Brussels over the coming months. This 
defaultsection 
defaulttherefore gives only an overview of the Direct Payments system, and reference may be made to the Status Report for further information.
