default Cross-Compliance is a set of rules that farmers claiming Direct Payments will have to comply with, as those claiming SPS currently do. Cross-Compliance comprises the need to comply with Statutory Management Requirements (SMRs) and to keep land in Good Agricultural and Environmental Condition (GAEC). Some changes to Cross-Compliance will result from the new CAP.
